[normal]4
[normal]8
[normal]All of the considerations above apply equally to women in industry, not least because we believe the nation would benefit if it was easy to move backwards and forwards between academia and industry during 
[normal]a
[normal] ca
[normal]reer.
[normal] These measures should be coordinated by a
[normal] body at the heart of the STEM academic/policy or funding community.
